{"tid":2050462,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"請連仔考慮加入圖片嵌入文字避mon po選項","createTime":"2020-06-04T06:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T08:19:26.000Z","uid":216441,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43a4005a8e333f82f241fd06194dcc21b56fcbe6","tid":2050462,"uid":216441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"今朝見到呢個po，入面講到可以寫code去generate啲電腦程式難以辨認嘅文字<br />\n<br />\n我想再加大mon po狗既監控成本<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2049871\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2049871</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n以往有其他會員曾經指出過政府係點樣mon po同埋記錄低邊個講<br />\n<br />\n[警告] 所有人必須用連登隱藏法去溝通<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331679\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331679</a><br />\n<br />\n加密可以令到非會員睇唔到講嘅野，不過同時亦都令好多cd rom睇唔到重要訊息，如果可以正式將呢個function加入就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3067ffc120df5629f1ada006995f851700bc430","tid":2050462,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T06:57:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7560dad2c085de5c821e5f39c1b5e50ab414205","tid":2050462,"uid":39734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"我驚個server 承受唔住..."},{"pid":"13ee484bdcb0c540c01b339a99fd2c6703013894","tid":2050462,"uid":44370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689c1668f0cca51633113c40043ec2a0cdf27b5d","tid":2050462,"uid":216441,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/04/145943_257cce992a0f572016bd55576c0021bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F